longBusinessSummary: Shen Yao Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the exploration and mining of gold deposits. It also manages hedge funds. The company was formerly known as LionGold Corp Ltd and changed its name to Shen Yao Holdings Limited in December 2020. Shen Yao Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Singapore.
